# To use a custom domain: rename this file to exactly "CNAME"
# (no extension), put ONLY your apex domain on the first line, e.g.
#     practicestreak.app
# then commit + push. Delete these comment lines — a real CNAME
# file must contain only the domain. Until you have a domain, leave
# this as CNAME.example and the site serves at the github.io URL.
